# Food Finder Project Architecture

food-finder/
├── client/
│   ├── public/
│   │   └── index.html            // Main HTML file for the client
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   ├── LocationComponent.jsx   // Gets user geolocation
│   │   │   ├── RestaurantList.jsx        // Displays nearby restaurants
│   │   │   ├── OrderInput.jsx            // Input for user food preferences
│   │   │   └── AnalyticsTracker.jsx      // Tracks user interactions
│   │   ├── App.jsx                       // Main app component
│   │   └── index.js                      // Entry point for client-side JS
│   ├── package.json                      // Client dependencies and scripts
│   └── .env                              // Client environment variables (if needed)
│
├── server/
│   ├── controllers/
│   │   ├── locationController.js         // Handles location-related requests
│   │   ├── orderController.js            // Handles order suggestion requests
│   │   └── analyticsController.js        // Processes analytics data
│   ├── routes/
│   │   ├── location.js                   // /location endpoints
│   │   ├── order.js                      // /order endpoints
│   │   └── analytics.js                  // /analytics endpoints
│   ├── services/
│   │   ├── googleApiService.js           // Integrates with Google Maps/Places API
│   │   ├── openaiService.js              // Integrates with OpenAI API
│   │   └── analyticsService.js           // Analytics data processing
│   ├── models/
│   │   └── analyticsModel.js             // Database schema/model for analytics
│   ├── app.js                            // Express app configuration
│   ├── server.js                         // Server entry point (starts the app)
│   ├── package.json                      // Server dependencies and scripts
│   └── .env                              // Server environment variables (API keys, etc.)
│
├── database/
│   ├── schema.sql                        // SQL schema/migration scripts
│   └── seed.js                           // Seed data for initial DB population
│
├── README.md                             // Project documentation
└── .gitignore                            // Files to ignore in git
